metadata.name: Golden Baboons Mining Club #1
metadata.description: The Golden Baboons Mining Club is a gold-backed NFT project from the publicly traded junior gold miner Asia Broadband. The company is backing each of the NFTS with a 1/2 gram of their gold reserves while the 10 1 of 1's will be backed by 1 ounce. The project has an Otherside Deed named Tequila Falls, where the Golden Baboons reside in the metaverse. For more on the project visit GoldenBaboons.com
